longBusinessSummary: John Mattson Fastighetsföretagen AB (publ) operates as a residential property owner in Sweden. It owns, develops, and manages rental apartments, as well as commercial premises and leasehold properties in municipalities, including Lidingö, Sollentuna, Stockholm, Nacka, and Upplands Väsby. The company was founded in 1945 and is headquartered in Lidingö, Sweden.
